I find that PoM xp is on par with what you would get in the planes. The mobs hit harder then PoP mobs of equivalent level. The named (not obvious names) all see invis nothing else does. Fairly low MR so easy to charm. Inside the castle (the bulk of zone) space can be limited so upto you if haste, CR is easy. Not found anything that cant be mezzed, pacified, rooted, or charmed except named. Loots are all no drop. Only the named will summon.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
